Except as expressly permitted in Section 2, You may NOT:

3.1 Commercial Distribution  
Sell, rent, lease, license, or otherwise commercially distribute the Project or any Derivative Work of the Project, whether alone or as part of a product or service, without the prior written permission of the copyright holder. This includes, without limitation:  
(a) selling access to downloads of the Project;  
(b) selling Modpacks in which the Project is a component;  
(c) including the Project in any paid software bundle, subscription, or similar commercial product.

Operating monetized servers in accordance with Section 2.2 is permitted and does not, by itself, constitute commercial distribution of the Project.

3.2 Public Release of Forks as Separate Projects  
Publicly release, advertise, or distribute any Derivative Work of the Project as an independent mod, modpack, or other product under a different name or branding, without the prior written permission of the copyright holder.

3.3 Re-licensing and Additional Restrictions  
